{"tid":324662,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得人種有冇優次之分？","createTime":"2017-07-16T15:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T10:22:08.000Z","uid":6988,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc26235eb49a08d4c2889dcdce5f9e458225156","tid":324662,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e48bcb399609e4cfbd42f566090fb12dd5f388","tid":324662,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5603cbc814c19f90d3c7c9b85f2d268fe8747cb7","tid":324662,"uid":28624,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:17:10.000Z","msg":"猶太人 最強智力<br />\n斯拉夫人 最強體質<br />\n支那人 最低劣垃圾基因人種"},{"pid":"8fbcb2b890388c59732c9614a82b69987f2b7242","tid":324662,"uid":6988,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>猶太人 最強智力<br />\n斯拉夫人 最強體質<br />\n支那人 最低劣垃圾基因人種</blockquote><br />\n梁啟超都有講過各國人種<br />\n「荷蘭，條頓民族之邦國人，其人情之忍耐節儉，勉於職業。葡萄牙，拉丁民族之邦國也，其人情之浮薄輕佻，其宗教為天主教，政治上之變化騷動甚多。條頓民族，其中軍也，斯拉夫民族，其後殿也。條頓民族，商人之性質，其腦髓所含者，算術也。至於斯拉夫民族，其事業非花非劇，非商非算，幽涼而沉雄，宏遠而堅毅。」"},{"pid":"279cdea51186246f119ab63808d7f110c1be7f67","tid":324662,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"問得呢個問題其實你自己已經有答案"},{"pid":"a8a7ad5e1bc067ef56c3dd70c97391fbcf473f6a","tid":324662,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問得呢個問題其實你自己已經有答案</blockquote><br />\n睇下大家意見姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d2d7b4257ac6de83a5d52d82c0bce16055d7ab","tid":324662,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re